For our annual Home & Design Issue, we check in with the ultimate tastemaker @mrshilfiger as she settles into her new #PalmBeach digs 

“We try to give a theme or personality to each home of ours. Our Miami home we called our weekend home, so we wanted it to be funky and fun... But this is now our home-home, where we reside full time. So we went a little less daring and more conservative. We still had fun—I think it’s quintessential Palm Beach, but at the same time, we brought a fresh and modern vibe to it.”
